subject: Rajasthan History
question_en: Which famous battle was fought between Maharaja Pratap and Mughal Emperor Akbar?
question_hi: महाराजा प्रताप और मुगल मुख्यालय आकर्ष के बीच काम किया गया क्या भी महान बैलेक्ट?
explanation_en: The Battle of Khanwa was fought between Maharana Pratap and Mughal Emperor Akbar. It took place on May 16, 1576, near Nagaur in Rajasthan.
